Cards:

Card component from bootstrap

On top splash image: 
Address for splash image for one hero, http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/img/champion/splash/Aatrox_0.jpg   
    Aatrox has to be changed out of the address to loop the address for every hero. You can do it by breaking the address up.

Name right under splash image to the left:
Address for names: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion.json
    data["data"][parameter]["name"];
    parameter has to be changed out

Badges beside the name to the right:
Address for the badges: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion.json
    data.data[parameter].tags[i];
    parameter has to be changed out in a loop and also i needs to be looped (nested)

Title under name:
Address for title: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion.json
    data["data"][parameter]["title"];
    parameter has to be changed out

Difficulty under title:
Address for difficulty: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion/Aatrox.json
    data["data"][parameter]["info"]["difficulty"];
    parameter has to be changed out
    display difficulty with the text; easy 1-3, average 4-6, hard 7-8, severe 9-10
    if(data["data"][parameter]["info"]["difficulty"] < 4 ){
        let difficultyEasy = "Easy";
    }
    if(data["data"][parameter]["info"]["difficulty"] > 3  && data["data"][parameter]["info"]["difficulty"] < 7){
        let difficultyAverage = "Average";
    }
    if(data["data"][parameter]["info"]["difficulty"] > 6 && data["data"][parameter]["info"]["difficulty"] < 9){
        let difficultyHard = "Hard";
    }
    if(data["data"][parameter]["info"]["difficulty"] > 8){
        let difficultySevere = "Severe";
    }



