Modal:

Modal component from bootstrap

Carousel in the top. It should fill out 2/3 of the modal space:
    Display all the skins in the carousel with the splash images
Address for the skin splash images: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion/Aatrox.json
    data.data[parameter].skins[i].num;
    parameter has to be changed out in a loop and also i needs to be looped (nested)
    Address for splash image for one hero, http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/img/champion/splash/Aatrox_0.jpg 
    Aatrox and the 0 has to be changed out of the address to loop the address for every hero. You can do it by breaking the address up.
        const champSplashAddressPrefix = "http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/img/champion/splash/"
        const champSplashAddressSuffix = ".jpg"
        {`${champSplashAddressPrefix}${CHAMPNAME}${NUM}${champSplashAddressSuffix}`}

Skin name in the top mid of carousel:
Address to skin name: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion/Aatrox.json
    Aatrox has to be changed out of the address to loop the address for every hero. You can do it by breaking the address up.
    data.data[parameter].skins[i].name;
    parameter has to be changed out in a loop and also i needs to be looped (nested)

Lore in the right corner of carousel on ONLY the first image:
Address for the lore: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion/Aatrox.json
    Aatrox has to be changed out of the address to loop the address for every hero. You can do it by breaking the address up.
    data.data[parameter].lore;
    parameter has to be changed out in a loop

Champion name under carousel to the left:
Address for names: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion.json
    data["data"][parameter]["name"];
    parameter has to be changed out

Badges beside the name to the right:
Address for the badges: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion.json
    data.data[parameter].tags[i];
    parameter has to be changed out in a loop and also i needs to be looped (nested)

Ally tips under champion name:
Address for ally tips: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion/Aatrox.json
    Aatrox has to be changed out of the address to loop the address for every hero. You can do it by breaking the address up.
    data.data[parameter].allytips[i];
    print it out in a <ul></ul>

Enemy tips under ally tips:
Address for ally tips: http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/10.13.1/data/en_US/champion/Aatrox.json
    Aatrox has to be changed out of the address to loop the address for every hero. You can do it by breaking the address up.
    data.data[parameter].enemytips[i];
    print it out in a <ul></ul>

